Sympathy Flowers
Delivery Details provided for:
Craig K Kempf Funeral Home and Cremation Services

Jensen B. Smith, infant son of Dustin Smith and Stevie Marie Linnabary of Tekonsha died Wednesday morning at Oaklawn Hospital in Marshall. He is survived by his parents; brothers, Camryn Ferman and Everett Smith; maternal grandmother, Kelley Linnabary of Battle Creek; great grandparents, Nancy LaFrance of Burlington and James Linnabary of Marshall; paternal grandparents, Lori Smith of Burlington and Johnnie B. Smith of Marshall and Ernie and Nancy Smith of Marshall; great grandparents, Pam and Leo Herman of Tekonsha; and great great grandparents, Howard and Mary Main of Tekonsha; and numerous aunts, uncles and cousins. Private family services were held in Riverside Cemetery in Tekonsha with Pastor Barbara Pryor of the Union United Church of Tekonsha officiating. Arrangements are by the Craig K. Kempf Funeral Home, Marshall.
